			<p class="chronoGuj"><img src="siteImages/anibook1.gif" width="30" height="24" alt="" border="0">&nbsp; કવિતાવિવેક (વિવેચન)</p>
			<p class="chronoGuj"><img src="siteImages/anibook1.gif" width="30" height="24" alt="" border="0">&nbsp; કાવ્યાનુશીલન (વિવેચન)</p>
